Sound Effects for Hearts
========================

Place the following OGG sound files in this directory:

- card-pickup.ogg  - Sound when picking up a card
- card-down.ogg    - Sound when placing a card
- card-shuffle.ogg - Sound when shuffling/dealing cards
- win.ogg          - Sound when winning a game
- lose.ogg         - Sound when losing a game

You can copy sounds from KPatience:
  /usr/share/kpat/sounds/

Or find free sounds at:
  - https://freesound.org/
  - https://opengameart.org/

The sounds should be installed to one of:
  - ./sounds/ (next to executable)
  - /usr/share/hearts/sounds/
  - ~/.local/share/hearts/sounds/
